-01-20T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcfb58f9c2ebd638160a38082f84640eb788089","tid":535293,"uid":92376,"like":46,"dislike":39,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-1-21 12:46am-10:46pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HScnebc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHScnebc.png&h=6e4838c4&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6qapKvQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6qapKvQ.png&h=eb7525f3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(10)周慧敏vs何雁詩(16)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"35015ac970bd1f962487cf7ff89b23fe98ed9a3e","tid":535293,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上半季籌到既296元已經捐出,多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱下半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/499662/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/499662/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃十六強抽籤結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/500805/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/500805/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃16強抽籤直播及結果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">16強賽序(前者先主場):<br />\nElizabeth Olsen v IU <br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月13日 3月7日 <br />\n<br />\nJennifer Lawrence v 周子瑜@TWICE<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月13日 3月7日 <br />\n<br />\nGal Gadot v 林娜璉@TWICE<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月14日 3月6日 <br />\n<br />\n唐嫣 v 新垣結衣<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月21日 3月13日 <br />\n<br />\n朱千雪 v 長澤正美<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月14日 3月6日 <br />\n<br />\nEmma Watson v 林宣妤<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月21日 3月13日 <br />\n<br />\n謝安琪 v 名井南@TWICE<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月20日 3月14日 <br />\n<br />\n平井桃@TWICE v 林明禎<br />\n首回合/次回合: 2月20日 3月14日 </span>"},{"pid":"eb61167312fc80d974a19eeeedc61bfa33af97ae","tid":535293,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3887a874a1dc3060268502a75c20b66caf1c71f9","tid":535293,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208135958f6984efe0279600c131579f4c18fac4","tid":535293,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acce37cc105e3fa4df14bfa20849c64b10dc8c6","tid":535293,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i